When you're planning on a long or international trip, you may want to consider a larger bag. Instead of buying another large travel bag, simply unzip the extra space of this bag and expand to as large as a 20in suitcase, stuff the excess into the bag, carry on and then go travel "light"

RAINY WEATHER SAFE - Made of water-resistant and anti-scratch nylon fabric, this duffel bag keeps gear dry if you get caught in a rain, a sudden downpour of snow or get coffee spilled during usual outings, especially important if there are electronic devices as part of your packed items

WET DRY SEPARATED - Equipped with a dedicated wet compartment, wet items, liquid or toiletries like wet towels, dirty clothes, shampoo or hairspay can be kept separately from dry belongings, plus the 8 pockets, a hygienic and organized travel is ready even without laundry access

AIRLINE CHARGE-FREE SIZE - Meets size allowance of most airlines. As a personal item or carry on, this bag holds everything you need from clothes to toiletries and fits perfectly under the seat or in the overhead bin. Save extra money for a check in bag

STYLISH MATCH FOR WOMEN - A detachable shoulder strap is included, this duffel bag has several carry options: tote bag, handbag, shoulder bag, crossbody bag. Whether you're going to the gym, the beach, city walk or on a trip, it matches your personal style well

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: As weekend or holiday comes, as sun rises up and sunshine pours onto the ground, it's time to start a trip and make our days again! But packing time of course stands ahead of the trip. Shirts, overcoats, beautiful dresses, pants, swimsuits, towel, umbrella, water bottle... SO MANY THINGS! What if the suitcase wheels can't work where I'm planning to?What if I have excessive luggage that can't be packed into the suitcase?What if my travel bag is too small? While carrying 2 or more bags are great pain and trouble.What if I have to buy a pile of gifts while my luggage bags are totally full? All these cases are not cases if you have a VPBAGE travel bag. It has extra 40% space expandable and is as roomy as a 20in suitcase. It acts as a stylish tote bag in daily uses, when you have additional packing needs, unzip the bottom then it's ready to go! When you need a standby bag, it can be folded to a "flat cake", won't take too much time in your luggage.

What if my car trunk is already full while I still have some other items to take along?What if I want to put my personal items under seat of airplane or bus? In these cases, the bag needs to be soft, so it can squash into any small corner or area. Meanwhile, it has to be scratch resistant to avoid wear during friction. More importantly, the fabric has to be easy to clean. No worries! VPBAGE has taken everything into consideration when designing this bag.

Another, this travel duffel bag can be used as a fashion tote bag in daily life and matches all dressing styles well! Then another thing, what if my coffee or drinks spill onto the bag? Will have a blue day with a dirty bag? DEFINITELY NO! The fabric is water-resistant and easy to clean. If any coffee splashes, just wipe it out with a wet towel or tissues. Besides, if you suddenly get caught in a light rain or snow, this tote bag would keep the gear dry and safe, especially useful when you have electronic in the bag, say, cellphone, tablet or earphone.
So are you looking for such a spacious, functional and clothes-matching duffel tote bag? If yes, what are you waiting for? Just add it to cart and make your days since today!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The best travel bag I've tried--what a champ
reviews.reviewText: After looking at probably 50 different carry-on bags, I decided on this one because it's more attractive than most and none of the reviews mentioned problems with the zippers. This is a very stylish bag, and it's well made--strong seams and hardware, sturdy zippers. It has just enough pockets to stash lots of small items you need en route, but not so many that you'll have to search for anything. The lighter colored lining makes it easy to find things, too. The shoulder strap is adjustable and comfortable.The size was just right for me. The bag held my laptop, a change of clothes, snacks, a windbreaker jacket, a book, a water bottle, a fairly large 35mm camera and lens, and a pair of shoes--and that was without being anywhere close to needing to use the bottom expansion feature. On the way to my destination, I used this as my carry-on bag (I had checked luggage). On the way home, I had additional items to pack and rather than overload my checked suitcase, I just expanded the bottom of this bag so I could redistribute my belongings--and I was still nowhere near filling it. I once again used this as a carry-on bag, which allowed me to use a small backpack as my personal item.During my trip, my bag got a lot of use and it got knocked around a bit, but it held up just fine. Considering the cream color, I expected the bag to get filthy, but it actually stayed quite clean. I'm really impressed with this bag and I only regret I didn't find it sooner for previous trips. As for the low price? I am shocked at what an exceptional value this is. I didn't expect to get something of this quality at that price.
